PhysicsBlend: Lets you manually control the physics/animation
bUpdateJointsFromAnimation: Lets you manually control the physics/animation
PhysicsUpdateMode: Determines whether simulation of root body updates component transform
PokePauseTime: Time between poking ragdoll and starting to blend back.
PokeBlendTime: Time taken to blend from physics to animation.
GravScale: Scale factor for the gravity used in the simulation
GravityOverrideZ: Gravity override used in the simulation
bUseGravityOverride: Toggle gravity override vs gravity scale
MaxFPS: Max FPS for simulation in PhysicsAssetEditor. This is helpful for targeting the same FPS as your game. -1 means disabled
HandleLinearDamping: Linear damping of mouse spring forces
HandleLinearStiffness: Linear stiffness of mouse spring forces
HandleAngularDamping: Angular damping of mouse spring forces
HandleAngularStiffness: Angular stiffness of mouse spring forces
InterpolationSpeed: How quickly we interpolate the physics target transform for mouse spring forces
PokeStrength: Strength of the impulse used when poking with left mouse button
InteractionDistance: Raycast distance when poking or grabbing
bResetClothWhenSimulating: When set, cloth will reset each time simulation is toggled
